    <title>Markdown的简单学习</title>
    <url>/2021/06/23/markdown/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="一级标题"><a href="#一级标题" class="headerlink" title="一级标题"></a>一级标题</h1><span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="二级"><a href="#二级" class="headerlink" title="二级"></a>二级</h2><h3 id="三级"><a href="#三级" class="headerlink" title="三级"></a>三级</h3><h4 id="四级"><a href="#四级" class="headerlink" title="四级"></a>四级</h4><h5 id="五级"><a href="#五级" class="headerlink" title="五级"></a>五级</h5><h6 id="六级"><a href="#六级" class="headerlink" title="六级"></a>六级</h6><p>正文直接输入就可以了</p>
<p>换行注意，要在代码中实际空出一行<br>直接换行的话，渲染输出其实是没有换行的</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">show ip interface brief</span><br><span class="line">router ospt Y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#x27;Hello World&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>正文中的代码<code>show ip interface trief</code></p>
<p>有序列表</p>
<ol>
<li>123</li>
<li>456</li>
<li>789<ol>
<li>123<ol>
<li>123<ol>
<li>123 </li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p>无序列表</p>
<ul>
<li>123<ul>
<li>123<ul>
<li>123</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>加粗</strong><br><em>倾斜</em><br><em><strong>加粗和倾斜</strong></em></p>
]]></content>
